{"tid":1981760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日黃昏有無手足有坐過東鐵","createTime":"2020-04-21T00:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T01:56:38.000Z","uid":220066,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea684a8455211c8ec48263ed3ea92fe89a29e9e8","tid":1981760,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"話說昨日放工大約6點半左右放工去紅磡<br />\n我坐緊東鐵(新車) M231 係頭等後面果卡<br />\n去到九龍塘站果陣有個黑衫黑褲既男人<br />\n係咁望住個後生仔按電話<br />\n又周圍轉不同位置去望呢個後生仔<br />\n最後列車差唔多去到紅磡站<br />\n佢更加想行前個後生仔面前<br />\n偷看個後生仔個電話按緊咩<br />\n唔知呢個人係咪黑警定公安<br />\n果個人眼神好來者不善<br />\n大家要小心出入安全<br />\n如非必要好似我咁坐黨鐵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：非鐵膠"},{"pid":"17c2162f4ac0cf97903ddc790fb4074811ddb175","tid":1981760,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ad1638536d2a0124ea634f07f7b337128a8e816","tid":1981760,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a1c63e074322e3e832d582c5f5b23346070e6cc","tid":1981760,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f26e678ad91289dc5f2ebbf8431668b5bdcfe00","tid":1981760,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:34:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"436877cf47c0b68c4ec4ef086092502bc0b06354","tid":1981760,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"你應該大聲喝條友『睇乜撚』嘛，又或者即時提醒位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會係尷尬，不過可以救返手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbef3332503a81b8080283eb5cdf4a77f90f1e2","tid":1981760,"uid":88133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"436877cf47c0b68c4ec4ef086092502bc0b06354","tid":1981760,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:38:5